summary:
A highly motivated and dedicated professional with a multicultural background that is
respectful of other cultures and traditions. Aside from teaching English I believe it is equally important to stimulate the development of intercultural understanding. Experienced in teaching both adolescents and adults from diverse backgrounds and various levels ranging from beginner to advanced. Knowledgeable in branches of language such as literature, (socio)linguistics, cross-culture understanding and more
